summary.en: Overall sentiment for SOL based on these whale movements is slightly bearish 🐻, primarily due to a net USDC outflow of $11,115 after accounting for other transactions. An interesting observation is the simultaneous $27,001 USDC inflow and outflow, which likely represents an internal transfer or rebalancing by a single entity. Despite the limited volume, the isolated outflow suggests a cautious stance among some whales. 🐳
summary.zh: 基于这些鲸鱼动向，SOL的整体情绪略显看跌 🐻，在扣除其他交易后，USDC净流出11,115美元。一个有趣的现象是同时发生的27,001美元USDC流入和流出，这可能代表单一实体的内部转移或再平衡。尽管交易量有限，但孤立的流出表明一些鲸鱼持谨慎态度。 🐳
